mal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />比個美國隊長你好唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n及至後來中大埋土既事，對家就係利用呢點分化曬外來人vs在校生呢樣野<br />\n在校生屌鳩外校人入黎破壞自己學校，外校人覺得自己比在校生當condom。一夜之間成功比對家分化<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />spin左個對立點去<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">本校生vs外來人</span><br />\n但其實呢樣野根本係錯鳩曬，要對立既應該係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">手足vs非手足</span></span><br />\n而呢個正正就係我一開始講既個樣野，我接觸唔曬所有人，但呢五個月黎我接觸既手足，無一個係會自己友傷自己友，無一個係會無差別傷人同破壞，我地並非藍絲。<br />\n而如果有個自稱手足而又用火魔掟鳩人，又亂吹風向無差別裝修破壞既，知咩事啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係要捉鬼，記住鬼係捉唔曬既，所以遇著有鬼/風向撚，要做既野係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一：自己心水清、自律；二：理撚得佢，冷處理</span><br />\n五個月啦，大把片影住班狗係街換曬black blk；著曬black blk由狗車接返狗屋，唔係未見過丫。<br />\n無可否認鬼係一定有，仲要係大撚把可能轉彎就撞到一個咁。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢樣野係我地一定要面對既問題，<br />\n係要大家團結，集思廣益拆搞掂佢，而唔係分化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我暫時諗到既野就係兩方面：一係文宣；二係自律，有其他方法歡迎大家再係下面討論。<br />\n<br />\n捉鬼捉唔完，捉鬼係唔可行。<br />\n我地只能靠<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">自律、謙虛</span>去防鬼<br />\n所以大家有意見分歧就一齊討論，有時d野一下子未做得好就認再慢慢改善，進化再進化！！唔好一唔岩聽就話人鬼話件風向撚，我地係香港人，我地係好清醒好humble架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不完美 可接受 要改善<br />\n但不割蓆 不分化呀<br />\n<br />\nSorry for 1999 and tldr <br />\n有咩大家一齊傾啦 唔好分化唔好割啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我愛你地每一個呀一個都不能少呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T20:32:31.000Z","msg":"sure ~<br />\n另外希望你睇下<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1725528/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1725528/page/1</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T20:36:37.000Z","msg":"做咩屌9 tsw 手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12fb61d202844f8716684707933ad1142edf8fec","tid":1725623,"uid":252368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T20:37:35.000Z","msg":"屌 <br />\n無人一出世就識抗爭<br />\n大家都係跌跌撞撞咁行過黎<br />\n唔識咪學<br />\n一黎就割<br />\n未撚開始就完左啦"},{"pid":"183d6a6ae73f2e59f313104c12aa933ff1838dd8","tid":1725623,"uid":252368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T20:40:05.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e666ce4c996ff2c12e2fd6e06007063721b321b","tid":1725623,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T20:40:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f07983ee21ac0edb9c5f0bb07e44880e3c95556","tid":1725623,"uid":252368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T20:43:16.000Z","msg":"無人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n毒撚平時都唔敢開po <br />\n真係好驚申家分化到先忍唔住要出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d77bdae02028761112bdb4bc67b964d1fd2f1cad","tid":1725623,"uid":252368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T20:43:51.000Z","msg":"手足我請你食一世熊仔餅（日版）"},{"pid":"d2c08cba5ed42031851e4b60bb842b219a7c54a2","tid":1725623,"uid":297997,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T20:44:01.000Z","msg":"敵人春袋痛了無棋了<br />\n<br />\n所以驚了<br />\n<br />\n要加速滲透再制造內訌<br />\n<br />\n先派出偽黃或者狗開post打好撚多字扮到語重深長懶係分析<br />\n<br />\n再有一堆五毛錢鳩衝係咁屌同分化<br />\n<br />\n再不停瘋狂鳩開post制造假象<br />\n<br />\n次次都同一招<br />\n<br />\n好撚悶<br />\n<br />\n唯有再渣實啲個春袋"},{"pid":"7049457ea6cf7309e7a1bd2293c8652bf395848f","tid":1725623,"uid":252368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T20:44:19.000Z","msg":"認真po 非標題黨真係無人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3caf3926e58382552b6d4e8918c0cc434457ce22","tid":1725623,"uid":126521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T20:45:20.000Z","msg":"推 互相尊重<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4306036686874e39917c1b83ddbba33fe0a8040","tid":1725623,"uid":252368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T20:45:48.000Z","msg":"To mon po狗 0.5<br />\n你地收皮啦 睇撚到曬你個狗樣啦"},{"pid":"aaaa4fa7f6a107694354d2c5d88321beb454501f","tid":1725623,"uid":126521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T20:45:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7086f7f35adc7b739efc9e377106044546264336","tid":1725623,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T20:46:32.000Z","msg":"推 be humble"},{"pid":"d1a9bbc6ceaa42f5e9fb8b4858ffb5968cc0d00f","tid":1725623,"uid":252368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T20:46:57.000Z","msg":"咁撚得閒上黎開po分化<br />\n不如醫左自己d氯痤瘡先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成身粒粒啦 仲要打字唔辛苦咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19cab8837854835569ac2bc1641274e5c3f36fc9","tid":1725623,"uid":126521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T20:47:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c33db1d04a700df929204b414bd89894e0c59541","tid":1725623,"uid":126521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T20:48:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76acbad3d332cee9655d619c6903efa4a1feb178","tid":1725623,"uid":252368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T20:49:44.000Z","msg":"Morning Sir！<br />\n小心tg後遺症呀 好擔心你地<br />\n你知你地架啦 日日放題 食得最多就係你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />陰公 心痛死人咩<br />\n有時間養下生啦 仲費神上黎分化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c586b98cb4547ca7f1cdb1c9851b5c0e81153bf7","tid":1725623,"uid":252368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T20:50:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fb53b203f091eb154e3027597c01ae77e840a3d","tid":1725623,"uid":126521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T20:51:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3014ee75d935d0542748aa4dffe61a2a4b2c8d47","tid":1725623,"uid":252368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T20:53:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf64eab4d6efda71fbf42a9fd80f0dbb3153be6b","tid":1725623,"uid":152938,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T20:54:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">勇武 不等於乜鳩都動武<br />\n講道理 唔代表你會變番和理非</span></span><br />\n唔該手足比番條底線自己 諗吓咩情況先要動武<br />\n係咪見倒有人撕幾張文宣就要打柒佢?<br />\n定係有個員工大嗌撐警就要幫佢裝修?<br />\n可能爭取自由民主嘅過程未必自由民主<br />\n但係爭取公義嘅手段應該要彰顯公義<br />\n同時守護道德嘅手段應該要符合道德底線"},{"pid":"78a69238b093875f891a4705a149d25550aaac24","tid":1725623,"uid":195158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f37ff82cfc2a9dadd879b04f40a788b8eb6d496","tid":1725623,"uid":252368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T20:23:13.000Z","msg":"見到咁撚多分化po就好撚嬲 屌<br />\n講一句先：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不分化不割蓆，但傷害同路人同無辜既一定唔係手足</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n首先，我地可唔可以唔好中對家計自己開始分化自己人<br />\n近日幾間大學既事就睇得出有人想開始割大學生/非大學生；本校人/外校人等等<br />\n其實，前線原本就唔淨止係由大學生組成，大把中學生，成年人，甚至有好多係你地口中既「mk仔」，而事實上手足係咩階層咩人都有，大家背景出身根本一開始就完全唔一樣，唯一相同既就係大家都係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有良心</span></span>先行出黎<br />\n識有d前線係話：「我讀書唔叻，粗人一個，但係有良心」佢地行到好前 甚至已經比人拉左charge左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你仲好意思同佢地割？人地唔同我地割已經偷笑。<br />\n利申讀緊U，但係好清楚大學不能成為大台，同時成場運動都不能只靠大學生 <br />\n見到有d人話「邊個邊個咁mk 講曬粗口 粗聲大氣咁 一定唔係大學生」我屌 講呢種說話既人自己本身有冇撚讀過U<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />根本大學入面都大把mk，你平時返學隔離個個唔mk咩？唔講粗口咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可唔可以唔好神化大學生呢個身分。we are one，我地係同路人無分高低架好唔好。<br />\n<br />\n然後，其實以上既野反映左一件事，就係大家心入面其實都潛在住一種<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">「任何事有少少缺點/我唔太中意啵，割蓆先」</span></strong></span>既傾向<br />\n（可能係風向撚，我自己認真左啦，唔清楚。但希望大家一直保持心水清）<br />\n其實由前排斬妖事件已經睇得出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解割我唔講啦，前排都睇得夠多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一有少少唔中意唔完美就割蓆，就捉鬼。人地個樣唔後生又話鬼，講野方式唔中意又話人地鬼，係咪睇戲睇上腦，正義既人一定又大隻又靚仔睇落又後生學歷又好高完美既，否則全部都係鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />比個美國隊長你好唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n及至後來中大埋土既事，對家就係利用呢點分化曬外來人vs在校生呢樣野<br />\n在校生屌鳩外校人入黎破壞自己學校，外校人覺得自己比在校生當condom。一夜之間成功比對家分化<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />spin左個對立點去<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">本校生vs外來人</span><br />\n但其實呢樣野根本係錯鳩曬，要對立既應該係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">手足vs非手足</span></span><br />\n而呢個正正就係我一開始講既個樣野，我接觸唔曬所有人，但呢五個月黎我接觸既手足，無一個係會自己友傷自己友，無一個係會無差別傷人同破壞，我地並非藍絲。<br />\n而如果有個自稱手足而又用火魔掟鳩人，又亂吹風向無差別裝修破壞既，知咩事啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係要捉鬼，記住鬼係捉唔曬既，所以遇著有鬼/風向撚，要做既野係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一：自己心水清、自律；二：理撚得佢，冷處理</span><br />\n五個月啦，大把片影住班狗係街換曬black blk；著曬black blk由狗車接返狗屋，唔係未見過丫。<br />\n無可否認鬼係一定有，仲要係大撚把可能轉彎就撞到一個咁。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢樣野係我地一定要面對既問題，<br />\n係要大家團結，集思廣益拆搞掂佢，而唔係分化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我暫時諗到既野就係兩方面：一係文宣；二係自律，有其他方法歡迎大家再係下面討論。<br />\n<br />\n捉鬼捉唔完，捉鬼係唔可行。<br />\n我地只能靠<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">自律、謙虛</span>去防鬼<br />\n所以大家有意見分歧就一齊討論，有時d野一下子未做得好就認再慢慢改善，進化再進化！！唔好一唔岩聽就話人鬼話件風向撚，我地係香港人，我地係好清醒好humble架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不完美 可接受 要改善<br />\n但不割蓆 不分化呀<br />\n<br />\nSorry for 1999 and tldr <br />\n有咩大家一齊傾啦 唔好分化唔好割啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我愛你地每一個呀一個都不能少呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T20:56:09.000Z","msg":"打仗靠威武同策略，修正隊型都達至提升「威」<br />\n<br />\n請入黎討論幫推<br />\n<br />\n[討論] 連登準聲明 不遵其一 居心可鑑<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1723330\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1723330</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c3feac4c3d08d5dc9f7e18525d6272be7b083077","tid":1725623,"uid":195158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T20:56:19.000Z","msg":"打仗靠威武同策略，修正隊型都達至提升「威」<br />\n<br />\n請入黎討論幫推<br />\n<br />\n[討論] 連登準聲明 不遵其一 居心可鑑<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1723330\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1723330</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"55b3a02ab3a00e63c7995b2a292cf265417a94e0","tid":1725623,"uid":93141,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T20:57:32.000Z","msg":"不傷害手足及無辜<br />\n不殺降兵<br />\n不立大台<br />\n不偷不搶不強姦<br />\n不送死<br />\n不打必敗之仗<br />\n不見死不救"},{"pid":"9af95cfe4a548b84c79bc0d465cfe73facb80170","tid":1725623,"uid":17733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T20:57:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"653c06d9f3953bd5231bdbac1be059a7fdc428e2","tid":1725623,"uid":252368,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bf64eab4d6efda71fbf42a9fd80f0dbb3153be6b","tid":1725623,"uid":152938,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T20:54:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">勇武 不等於乜鳩都動武<br />\n講道理 唔代表你會變番和理非</span></span><br />\n唔該手足比番條底線自己 諗吓咩情況先要動武<br />\n係咪見倒有人撕幾張文宣就要打柒佢?<br />\n定係有個員工大嗌撐警就要幫佢裝修?<br />\n可能爭取自由民主嘅過程未必自由民主<br />\n但係爭取公義嘅手段應該要彰顯公義<br />\n同時守護道德嘅手段應該要符合道德底線"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T20:59:58.000Z","msg":"屌 真<br />\n勇武叫勇武唔係代表佢地有勇無謀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n平時見好多勇武對同路人/婆婆小朋友係極好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n相信真手足係會聽意見 係有底線<br />\n如果係狗係鬼既 死撚開啦返狗屋慢慢生滋啦"},{"pid":"2071eed9c6415322339f84d51558497d620b5a48","tid":1725623,"uid":109115,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T21:00:00.000Z","msg":"希望大家能夠繼續自我修正<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c5ab78a0b0bb5268af733d2829c3ef49f7c7420","tid":1725623,"uid":266755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f37ff82cfc2a9dadd879b04f40a788b8eb6d496","tid":1725623,"uid":252368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T20:23:13.000Z","msg":"見到咁撚多分化po就好撚嬲 屌<br />\n講一句先：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不分化不割蓆，但傷害同路人同無辜既一定唔係手足</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n首先，我地可唔可以唔好中對家計自己開始分化自己人<br />\n近日幾間大學既事就睇得出有人想開始割大學生/非大學生；本校人/外校人等等<br />\n其實，前線原本就唔淨止係由大學生組成，大把中學生，成年人，甚至有好多係你地口中既「mk仔」，而事實上手足係咩階層咩人都有，大家背景出身根本一開始就完全唔一樣，唯一相同既就係大家都係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有良心</span></span>先行出黎<br />\n識有d前線係話：「我讀書唔叻，粗人一個，但係有良心」佢地行到好前 甚至已經比人拉左charge左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你仲好意思同佢地割？人地唔同我地割已經偷笑。<br />\n利申讀緊U，但係好清楚大學不能成為大台，同時成場運動都不能只靠大學生 <br />\n見到有d人話「邊個邊個咁mk 講曬粗口 粗聲大氣咁 一定唔係大學生」我屌 講呢種說話既人自己本身有冇撚讀過U<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />根本大學入面都大把mk，你平時返學隔離個個唔mk咩？唔講粗口咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可唔可以唔好神化大學生呢個身分。we are one，我地係同路人無分高低架好唔好。<br />\n<br />\n然後，其實以上既野反映左一件事，就係大家心入面其實都潛在住一種<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">「任何事有少少缺點/我唔太中意啵，割蓆先」</span></strong></span>既傾向<br />\n（可能係風向撚，我自己認真左啦，唔清楚。但希望大家一直保持心水清）<br />\n其實由前排斬妖事件已經睇得出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解割我唔講啦，前排都睇得夠多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一有少少唔中意唔完美就割蓆，就捉鬼。人地個樣唔後生又話鬼，講野方式唔中意又話人地鬼，係咪睇戲睇上腦，正義既人一定又大隻又靚仔睇落又後生學歷又好高完美既，否則全部都係鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />比個美國隊長你好唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n及至後來中大埋土既事，對家就係利用呢點分化曬外來人vs在校生呢樣野<br />\n在校生屌鳩外校人入黎破壞自己學校，外校人覺得自己比在校生當condom。一夜之間成功比對家分化<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />spin左個對立點去<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">本校生vs外來人</span><br />\n但其實呢樣野根本係錯鳩曬，要對立既應該係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">手足vs非手足</span></span><br />\n而呢個正正就係我一開始講既個樣野，我接觸唔曬所有人，但呢五個月黎我接觸既手足，無一個係會自己友傷自己友，無一個係會無差別傷人同破壞，我地並非藍絲。<br />\n而如果有個自稱手足而又用火魔掟鳩人，又亂吹風向無差別裝修破壞既，知咩事啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係要捉鬼，記住鬼係捉唔曬既，所以遇著有鬼/風向撚，要做既野係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一：自己心水清、自律；二：理撚得佢，冷處理</span><br />\n五個月啦，大把片影住班狗係街換曬black blk；著曬black blk由狗車接返狗屋，唔係未見過丫。<br />\n無可否認鬼係一定有，仲要係大撚把可能轉彎就撞到一個咁。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢樣野係我地一定要面對既問題，<br />\n係要大家團結，集思廣益拆搞掂佢，而唔係分化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我暫時諗到既野就係兩方面：一係文宣；二係自律，有其他方法歡迎大家再係下面討論。<br />\n<br />\n捉鬼捉唔完，捉鬼係唔可行。<br />\n我地只能靠<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">自律、謙虛</span>去防鬼<br />\n所以大家有意見分歧就一齊討論，有時d野一下子未做得好就認再慢慢改善，進化再進化！！唔好一唔岩聽就話人鬼話件風向撚，我地係香港人，我地係好清醒好humble架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不完美 可接受 要改善<br />\n但不割蓆 不分化呀<br />\n<br />\nSorry for 1999 and tldr <br />\n有咩大家一齊傾啦 唔好分化唔好割啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我愛你地每一個呀一個都不能少呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T21:00:35.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"58bbc3148a2064a474b4d73aaeb02080d6e72599","tid":1725623,"uid":297997,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T21:00:48.000Z","msg":"敵人春袋痛了無棋了<br />\n<br />\n中大，大學站，吐露港春袋好痛<br />\n<br />\n東鐵死，吐露港物流死，蝗無得嚟香港<br />\n<br />\n所以驚了<br />\n<br />\n要加速滲透再制造內訌<br />\n<br />\n先派出偽黃或者狗開post打好撚多字扮到語重深長懶係分析<br />\n<br />\n再有一堆五毛鳩衝係咁屌同分化<br />\n<br />\n吹失敗，散水風向，屌手足<br />\n<br />\n再不停瘋狂鳩開post制造假象<br />\n<br />\n次次都同一招<br />\n<br />\n好撚悶<br />\n<br />\n勿忘不被分化不割𥱊不完美再改善"},{"pid":"b5fbbe498afe685f2f47c76441f921577dd77451","tid":1725623,"uid":252368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"78a69238b093875f891a4705a149d25550aaac24","tid":1725623,"uid":195158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f37ff82cfc2a9dadd879b04f40a788b8eb6d496","tid":1725623,"uid":252368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T20:23:13.000Z","msg":"見到咁撚多分化po就好撚嬲 屌<br />\n講一句先：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不分化不割蓆，但傷害同路人同無辜既一定唔係手足</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n首先，我地可唔可以唔好中對家計自己開始分化自己人<br />\n近日幾間大學既事就睇得出有人想開始割大學生/非大學生；本校人/外校人等等<br />\n其實，前線原本就唔淨止係由大學生組成，大把中學生，成年人，甚至有好多係你地口中既「mk仔」，而事實上手足係咩階層咩人都有，大家背景出身根本一開始就完全唔一樣，唯一相同既就係大家都係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有良心</span></span>先行出黎<br />\n識有d前線係話：「我讀書唔叻，粗人一個，但係有良心」佢地行到好前 甚至已經比人拉左charge左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你仲好意思同佢地割？人地唔同我地割已經偷笑。<br />\n利申讀緊U，但係好清楚大學不能成為大台，同時成場運動都不能只靠大學生 <br />\n見到有d人話「邊個邊個咁mk 講曬粗口 粗聲大氣咁 一定唔係大學生」我屌 講呢種說話既人自己本身有冇撚讀過U<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />根本大學入面都大把mk，你平時返學隔離個個唔mk咩？唔講粗口咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可唔可以唔好神化大學生呢個身分。we are one，我地係同路人無分高低架好唔好。<br />\n<br />\n然後，其實以上既野反映左一件事，就係大家心入面其實都潛在住一種<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">「任何事有少少缺點/我唔太中意啵，割蓆先」</span></strong></span>既傾向<br />\n（可能係風向撚，我自己認真左啦，唔清楚。但希望大家一直保持心水清）<br />\n其實由前排斬妖事件已經睇得出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解割我唔講啦，前排都睇得夠多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一有少少唔中意唔完美就割蓆，就捉鬼。人地個樣唔後生又話鬼，講野方式唔中意又話人地鬼，係咪睇戲睇上腦，正義既人一定又大隻又靚仔睇落又後生學歷又好高完美既，否則全部都係鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />比個美國隊長你好唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n及至後來中大埋土既事，對家就係利用呢點分化曬外來人vs在校生呢樣野<br />\n在校生屌鳩外校人入黎破壞自己學校，外校人覺得自己比在校生當condom。一夜之間成功比對家分化<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />spin左個對立點去<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">本校生vs外來人</span><br />\n但其實呢樣野根本係錯鳩曬，要對立既應該係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">手足vs非手足</span></span><br />\n而呢個正正就係我一開始講既個樣野，我接觸唔曬所有人，但呢五個月黎我接觸既手足，無一個係會自己友傷自己友，無一個係會無差別傷人同破壞，我地並非藍絲。<br />\n而如果有個自稱手足而又用火魔掟鳩人，又亂吹風向無差別裝修破壞既，知咩事啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係要捉鬼，記住鬼係捉唔曬既，所以遇著有鬼/風向撚，要做既野係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一：自己心水清、自律；二：理撚得佢，冷處理</span><br />\n五個月啦，大把片影住班狗係街換曬black blk；著曬black blk由狗車接返狗屋，唔係未見過丫。<br />\n無可否認鬼係一定有，仲要係大撚把可能轉彎就撞到一個咁。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢樣野係我地一定要面對既問題，<br />\n係要大家團結，集思廣益拆搞掂佢，而唔係分化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我暫時諗到既野就係兩方面：一係文宣；二係自律，有其他方法歡迎大家再係下面討論。<br />\n<br />\n捉鬼捉唔完，捉鬼係唔可行。<br />\n我地只能靠<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">自律、謙虛</span>去防鬼<br />\n所以大家有意見分歧就一齊討論，有時d野一下子未做得好就認再慢慢改善，進化再進化！！唔好一唔岩聽就話人鬼話件風向撚，我地係香港人，我地係好清醒好humble架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不完美 可接受 要改善<br />\n但不割蓆 不分化呀<br />\n<br />\nSorry for 1999 and tldr <br />\n有咩大家一齊傾啦 唔好分化唔好割啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我愛你地每一個呀一個都不能少呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T20:56:09.000Z","msg":"打仗靠威武同策略，修正隊型都達至提升「威」<br />\n<br />\n請入黎討論幫推<br />\n<br />\n[討論] 連登準聲明 不遵其一 居心可鑑<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1723330\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1723330</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T21:01:27.000Z","msg":"可能要推一個聲明出黎<br />\n文宣一下<br />\n我地係有底線有良心既<br />\nWhich is係狗扮唔黎既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90cc4ad9826a866d5508fefde140fe52fa4f03a3","tid":1725623,"uid":252368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2071eed9c6415322339f84d51558497d620b5a48","tid":1725623,"uid":109115,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T21:00:00.000Z","msg":"希望大家能夠繼續自我修正<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T21:02:39.000Z","msg":"Yes 過去五個月辛苦曬大家啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家都好叻<br />\n一定會繼續進化落去！！"},{"pid":"0903456625739090cf7d8031ee691203b6cfa922","tid":1725623,"uid":252368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"58bbc3148a2064a474b4d73aaeb02080d6e72599","tid":1725623,"uid":297997,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T21:00:48.000Z","msg":"敵人春袋痛了無棋了<br />\n<br />\n中大，大學站，吐露港春袋好痛<br />\n<br />\n東鐵死，吐露港物流死，蝗無得嚟香港<br />\n<br />\n所以驚了<br />\n<br />\n要加速滲透再制造內訌<br />\n<br />\n先派出偽黃或者狗開post打好撚多字扮到語重深長懶係分析<br />\n<br />\n再有一堆五毛鳩衝係咁屌同分化<br />\n<br />\n吹失敗，散水風向，屌手足<br />\n<br />\n再不停瘋狂鳩開post制造假象<br />\n<br />\n次次都同一招<br />\n<br />\n好撚悶<br />\n<br />\n勿忘不被分化不割𥱊不完美再改善"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T21:04:10.000Z","msg":"建議mon po滲透分化狗返屋企醫下d滋先"},{"pid":"b0ee53879e093cd33c5852e6ec53b02ebb7d835a","tid":1725623,"uid":297997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0903456625739090cf7d8031ee691203b6cfa922","tid":1725623,"uid":252368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"58bbc3148a2064a474b4d73aaeb02080d6e72599","tid":1725623,"uid":297997,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T21:00:48.000Z","msg":"敵人春袋痛了無棋了<br />\n<br />\n中大，大學站，吐露港春袋好痛<br />\n<br />\n東鐵死，吐露港物流死，蝗無得嚟香港<br />\n<br />\n所以驚了<br />\n<br />\n要加速滲透再制造內訌<br />\n<br />\n先派出偽黃或者狗開post打好撚多字扮到語重深長懶係分析<br />\n<br />\n再有一堆五毛鳩衝係咁屌同分化<br />\n<br />\n吹失敗，散水風向，屌手足<br />\n<br />\n再不停瘋狂鳩開post制造假象<br />\n<br />\n次次都同一招<br />\n<br />\n好撚悶<br />\n<br />\n勿忘不被分化不割𥱊不完美再改善"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T21:04:10.000Z","msg":"建議mon po滲透分化狗返屋企醫下d滋先"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T21:05:23.000Z","msg":"無得返<br />\n<br />\n狗乸同大sir床戰緊"},{"pid":"4ab68bf71d6e3770f7cfa596b1d77d9d98d83923","tid":1725623,"uid":252368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T21:06:37.000Z","msg":"停止標籤同分化同路人！！！<br />\nMk就唔可以有良心唔可以抗爭咩<br />\n我係毒撚我係咪又唔可以叫口號<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dfbb7dceee8059da2f62b263e8e92f186be4309","tid":1725623,"uid":82175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T21:10:04.000Z","msg":"控制自己武力"},{"pid":"41518975112284aa3f2ae36f3031e9e6254eaa84","tid":1725623,"uid":304663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T21:11:21.000Z","msg":"頂住呀 就win 嫁啦"},{"pid":"8492a8dd30f8